data.title: Schäfersfeld
data.meta_description: The Schäfersfeld is a col with a length of 4.5 kilometer. This is a category 2 col. It is located in Bad Peterstal Griesbach, Baden-Württemberg, Germany. The average grade of this col is 8.5% with a maximum of 10.7%. The Schäfersfeld ascents from 360 meter at the start, to 758 meter at the top, with a total of 397 ascending meters.
